card.title: Captain Underpants and the Invasion of the Incredibly Naughty Cafeteria Ladies from Outer Space

metadata.description: George and Harold have played a trick or two on nearly everyone at Jerome Horwitz Elementary. When their latest prank causes the school's cranky cafeteria ladies to quit, Mr. Krupp hires a trio of unusual replacements — who happen to look an awful lot like aliens! Will that curtain-caped crusader, Captain Underpants, save the day once more? Or will those outer-space cafeteria ladies have him for lunch?
metadata.author: Dav Pilkey
